General.Description: Speqta AB (publ), an Adtech company, provides traffic generating services in eCommerce using data and AI. The company's services include The Affiliate network Shopello, the SaaS service Bidbrain, and the SaaS service BrightBid. The company is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
